        "description": {
          "value": "<p>You enter a stance of fluid two-weapon grace. While in this stance, when you make your second attack with an agile one-handed weapon in your off-hand, it doesn't take the multiple attack penalty.</p>"
        },
        "featType": { "value": "class" },
